                <h2>What is the Turtle Shelter Project?</h2>
                <p>Every winter, thousands of homeless individuals face life-threatening cold. We have a solution: a portable, lightweight shelter that can be carried like a turtle’s shell.
                    Crafted with advanced foam technology, the vest traps body heat, providing warmth and protection from hypothermia and frostbite in freezing temperatures.
                    By volunteering to help craft these vests, you’re not just providing warmth – you’re giving hope to those without a home. Every vest you help distribute could save a life. Be the difference between survival and suffering this winter.</p>
